Go to x dashboard.
Click the three dots on the top right and click &ldquo;Save As&rdquo;
Name the Dashboard starting with your three intitials, e.g. &ldquo;SEW Digital Experience&rdquo;
Save to your dashboard group.
Change the filter to include tests with your initials &ldquo;test=SEW*&rdquo;
Open the table chart to see how this was made, and feel free to add/remove other tests and metrics as you&rsquo;d like.
Compare to other websites Create one or more Synthetic Browser Tests on your competitors&rsquo; websites, with your initials in the title of the tests.
